Discounts at local athletics facilities
If qualified, no-fee investment opportunities in TFS-managed private funds

 
*Please note that benefits are subject to change and may vary by employee. Presently TFS Capital pays a portion of health and dental insurance. Employees are generally eligible for the TFS profit-sharing-plan after two years of employment.





