TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Market Neutral Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 7:53 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Market Neutral Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Market Neutral Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by TFS Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It takes long and short positions to invest directly and indirectly through derivatives like futures in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations with a focus on small-cap companies. It employs a market neutral strategy to create its portfolio. The fund employs quantitative analysis while focusing on factors like fundamental and technical variables, data from company financial or management fi...
TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Market Neutral Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by TFS Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It takes long and short positions to invest directly and indirectly through derivatives like futures in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations with a focus on small-cap companies. It employs a market neutral strategy to create its portfolio. The fund employs quantitative analysis while focusing on factors like fundamental and technical variables, data from company financial or management filings, trade data across various markets and price movements to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Standard & Poor’s 500 Index. The fund conducts proprietary research to create its portfolio. TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Market Neutral Fund was formed on September 7, 2004 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


