TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Small Cap Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 7:53 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Small Cap Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Small Cap Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by TFS Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap companies, with market capitalization within the range of the Russell 2000 Index. It employs quantitative analysis focusing on factors like fundamental and technical variables, including data from company financial or management filings, trade data across various markets and price movements to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its ...
TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Small Cap Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by TFS Capital LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap companies, with market capitalization within the range of the Russell 2000 Index. It employs quantitative analysis focusing on factors like fundamental and technical variables, including data from company financial or management filings, trade data across various markets and price movements to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Index. It conducts proprietary research to create its portfolio. TFS Capital Investment Trust - TFS Small Cap Fund was formed on March 7, 2006 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


10 North High StreetSuite 500West Chester, PA 19380United StatesFounded in 2006



Phone: 888-837-4446

Fax: 610-719-8376

